{"tid":849051,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【人間蒸發】國際刑警組織主席孟宏偉返國失蹤 法警追查下落","createTime":"2018-10-05T11:35:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-05T11:52:01.000Z","uid":40401,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7268fd90fa4b0bf42b1bdecd621e570e13c82851","tid":849051,"uid":40401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T11:35:37.000Z","msg":"法國警方透露，將會就國際刑警組織（Interpol）主席孟宏偉（64歲）失蹤展開調查。據報，孟宏偉中國公安部副部長，上周飛返中國期間據報失蹤。<br />\n<br />\n法新社及路透社今日引述警方消息指，孟宏偉與妻兒居住在法國里昂，自9月29日前赴中國時，就失去其消息，家人也無法聯絡他，也未能確定其身處位置。<br />\n<br />\n孟宏偉於2016年11月當選新一任國際刑警組織主席，主要負責國際追逃追贓工作，更成為首個當選國際刑警組織主席的中國人，任期至2020年才告屆滿。但有人權組織擔心，北京可能利用該組織追捕外逃的異見人士。<br />\n<br />\n國際刑警組織暫時未就孟宏偉失蹤一事作出回應。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20181005&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=58760901\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20181005%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D58760901&d=dzHijIxb1BJdM2dR2xKuSf7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=b19be141\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20181005%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D58760901&h=c5445241\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20181005&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=58760901</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00799d0cb579577682bc2423a1b0d3368cd551f2","tid":849051,"uid":40401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T11:36:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6d353c3944f01b91239e1bb09a2990665527bea","tid":849051,"uid":40401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T11:39:18.000Z","msg":"